'''Yuri Lowenthal''' is an American actor and voice actor, best known for voicing The Prince in the ''Prince of Persia'' video game series.

In ''[[Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series]]'', he voices [[Tom (Telltale)|Tom]], [[Erik]] and [[Finn]].
